// essence of laves graph intertwined

// Visualization of one unit voxel (fundamental cell) of the
// [url]https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laves_graph[/url].
// Colored to emphasize permutation symmetry.

// tags: raymarch, sdf, voxel, distance, graph, field, mesh, signed, unit, laves, intertwine

